{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 52,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الطُّورِ",
    "englishName": "At-Tur",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Mount",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 49,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 4736,
        "text": "By the Mount (of Revelation);",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4737,
        "text": "By a Decree inscribed",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4738,
        "text": "In a Scroll unfolded;",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4739,
        "text": "By the much-frequented Fane;",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4740,
        "text": "By the Canopy Raised High;",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4741,
        "text": "And by the Ocean filled with Swell;-",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4742,
        "text": "Verily, the Doom of thy Lord will indeed come to pass;-",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4743,
        "text": "There is none can avert it;-",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4744,
        "text": "On the Day when the firmament will be in dreadful commotion.",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4745,
        "text": "And the mountains will fly hither and thither.",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4746,
        "text": "Then woe that Day to those that treat (Truth) as Falsehood;-",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4747,
        "text": "That play (and paddle) in shallow trifles.",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4748,
        "text": "That Day shall they be thrust down to the Fire of Hell, irresistibly.",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4749,
        "text": "\"This:, it will be said, \"Is the Fire,- which ye were wont to deny!",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4750,
        "text": "\"Is this then a fake, or is it ye that do not see?",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4751,
        "text": "\"Burn ye therein: the same is it to you whether ye bear it with patience, or not: Ye but receive the recompense of your (own) deeds.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4752,
        "text": "As to the Righteous, they will be in Gardens, and in Happiness,-",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4753,
        "text": "Enjoying the (Bliss) which their Lord hath bestowed on them, and their Lord shall deliver them from the Penalty of the Fire.",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4754,
        "text": "(To them will be said:) \"Eat and drink ye, with profit and health, because of your (good) deeds.\"",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4755,
        "text": "They will recline (with ease) on Thrones (of dignity) arranged in ranks; and We shall join them to Companions, with beautiful big and lustrous eyes.",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4756,
        "text": "And those who believe and whose families follow them in Faith,- to them shall We join their families: Nor shall We deprive them (of the fruit) of aught of their works: (Yet) is each individual in pledge for his deeds.",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4757,
        "text": "And We shall bestow on them, of fruit and meat, anything they shall desire.",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4758,
        "text": "They shall there exchange, one with another, a (loving) cup free of frivolity, free of all taint of ill.",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4759,
        "text": "Round about them will serve, (devoted) to them, young male servants (handsome) as Pearls well-guarded.",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4760,
        "text": "They will advance to each other, engaging in mutual enquiry.",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4761,
        "text": "They will say: \"Aforetime, we were not without fear for the sake of our people.",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4762,
        "text": "\"But Allah has been good to us, and has delivered us from the Penalty of the Scorching Wind.",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4763,
        "text": "\"Truly, we did call unto Him from of old: truly it is He, the Beneficent, the Merciful!\"",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 458,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4764,
        "text": "Therefore proclaim thou the praises (of thy Lord): for by the Grace of thy Lord, thou art no (vulgar) soothsayer, nor art thou one possessed.",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4765,
        "text": "Or do they say:- \"A Poet! we await for him some calamity (hatched) by Time!\"",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4766,
        "text": "Say thou: \"Await ye!- I too will wait along with you!\"",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 524,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4767,
        "text": "Is it that their faculties of understanding urge them to this, or are they but a people transgressing beyond bounds?",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4768,
        "text": "Or do they say, \"He fabricated the (Message)\"? Nay, they have no faith!",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4769,
        "text": "Let them then produce a recital like unto it,- If (it be) they speak the truth!",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4770,
        "text": "Were they created of nothing, or were they themselves the creators?",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4771,
        "text": "Or did they create the heavens and the earth? Nay, they have no firm belief.",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4772,
        "text": "Or are the Treasures of thy Lord with them, or are they the managers (of affairs)?",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4773,
        "text": "Or have they a ladder, by which they can (climb up to heaven and) listen (to its secrets)? Then let (such a) listener of theirs produce a manifest proof.",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4774,
        "text": "Or has He only daughters and ye have sons?",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4775,
        "text": "Or is it that thou dost ask for a reward, so that they are burdened with a load of debt?-",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4776,
        "text": "Or that the Unseen in it their hands, and they write it down?",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4777,
        "text": "Or do they intend a plot (against thee)? But those who defy Allah are themselves involved in a Plot!",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4778,
        "text": "Or have they a god other than Allah? Exalted is Allah far above the things they associate with Him!",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4779,
        "text": "Were they to see a piece of the sky falling (on them), they would (only) say: \"Clouds gathered in heaps!\"",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4780,
        "text": "So leave them alone until they encounter that Day of theirs, wherein they shall (perforce) swoon (with terror),-",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4781,
        "text": "The Day when their plotting will avail them nothing and no help shall be given them.",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4782,
        "text": "And verily, for those who do wrong, there is another punishment besides this: But most of them understand not.",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4783,
        "text": "Now await in patience the command of thy Lord: for verily thou art in Our eyes: and celebrate the praises of thy Lord the while thou standest forth,",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4784,
        "text": "And for part of the night also praise thou Him,- and at the retreat of the stars!",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 525,
        "ruku": 459,
        "hizbQuarter": 210,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
